===停產===
2020年9月16日，任天堂在其日本官網上宣佈3DS、3DSLL及2DS三款遊戲機終止生產<ref name=itmedia-20200917>{{cite news |url=https://www.itmedia.co.jp/news/articles/2009/17/news125.html |title=ニンテンドー3DSが生産終了　「2DS」「LL」など関連モデルも |publisher=ITmedia |date=2020-09-17 |language=ja |accessdate=2020-09-18 |archive-date=2021-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205075810/https://www.itmedia.co.jp/news/articles/2009/17/news125.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2DS從問世到2018年9月30日於全球銷售約968萬套<ref name="nintendo.co.jp">{{cite web |url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/pdf/2018/181030e.pdf |title=Nintendo Co., Ltd. Earnings Release: Six Months Ended September 30, 2018 |date=2018-10-30 |publisher=Nintendo |page=8 |format=PDF |accessdate=2019-01-06 |archive-date=2021-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212093249/https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/pdf/2018/181030e.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。3DS、2DS系列停產後，該公司只剩下Switch一款遊戲機系列生產銷售中<ref name=yahoojp-58a5 />。

== 硬體 ==
{{see also|任天堂3DS#硬件|l1=任天堂3DS的硬件}}
任天堂2DS的硬件规格几乎和任天堂3DS相同；保留的特性如GPU、CPU和内存，以及对任天堂DS和任天堂3DS游戏设计的兼容性。但其硬件还是略有差别。和之前机种的设计明显不同。

和使用双显示屏，上屏能够显示[[裸眼立体|裸眼3D]]的任天堂3DS不同，其屏幕并不是分开的两块，而是整个一块电阻触控LCD屏，并使用外框将屏幕尺寸遮盖到3DS那样的大小<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-10-16-this-is-what-the-2ds-huge-single-lcd-screen-looks-like|title=This is what the 2DS' huge single LCD screen looks like|accessdate=2013-11-10|publisher=Eurogamer|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030203922/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-10-16-this-is-what-the-2ds-huge-single-lcd-screen-looks-like|dead-url=no}}</ref>。通过这种方式，任天堂节省去了不必要的元件。为了让上屏不能进行触控操作而下屏可以，任天堂在上屏的区域加上了一块塑料板进行覆盖。这就和这代游戏机所应该有的机能一样了<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.usgamer.net/articles/oh-so-thats-nintendos-next-move|title=Oh, So That's Nintendo's Next Move|accessdate=2017-06-20|last=Parish|first=Jeremy|work=USgamer|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170629134730/http://www.usgamer.net/articles/oh-so-thats-nintendos-next-move|archive-date=2017-06-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。虽然2DS无法显示3D内容，但其保留了3DS能拍摄3D格式相片的[[立体摄像机|双摄像头]]<ref name="ars">{{cite web | url=http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2013/08/how-the-2ds-could-have-been-nintendos-first-true-portable-tablet/ | title=How the 2DS could have been Nintendo’s first true portable tablet | publisher=Condé Nast Digital | work=Ars Technica | accessdate=2013-08-29 | last=Orland | first=Kyle | archive-date=2013-08-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130830011026/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2013/08/how-the-2ds-could-have-been-nintendos-first-true-portable-tablet/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。不同于3DS的内置[[立体声|立体声]]扬声器，任天堂2DS只有内置[[单声道|单声道]]扬声器，但通过耳机插孔依然可以输入立体声<ref name="Kotaku announcement" />。

虽然大小大致相同，但2DS使用了“直板”式设计，而非DS和3DS的[[翻盖|翻盖]]。其按键放置于设备中部，而非在下屏底部附近。侧肩按钮则为凹面且比3DS的更厚。代之于合盖操作，2DS通过开关进入[[睡眠模式|睡眠模式]]，硬件无线开关则改为软件开关<ref name="Kotaku announcement" /><ref name="polygon">{{cite web|title=Nintendo 2DS hands-on: surprisingly not the worst thing ever|url=http://www.polygon.com/2013/8/30/4676984/nintendo-2ds-hands-on-surprisingly-not-the-worst-thing-ever|work=Polygon|publisher=Vox Media|accessdate=2014-01-17|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112023423/http://www.polygon.com/2013/8/30/4676984/nintendo-2ds-hands-on-surprisingly-not-the-worst-thing-ever|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="wp-release">{{cite web|url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/business/technology/nintendo-drops-wii-u-price-releases-new-2ds-handheld/2013/08/28/da9d53be-0ff9-11e3-8cdd-bcdc09410972_story.html|title = Nintendo drops Wii U price, releases new ‘2DS’ handheld|last = Tsukayama|first = Hayley|publisher = The Washington Post|date = |accessdate = 2013-08-20|archive-date = 2019-06-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190628081351/https://www.washingtonpost.com/business/technology/nintendo-drops-wii-u-price-releases-new-2ds-handheld/2013/08/28/da9d53be-0ff9-11e3-8cdd-bcdc09410972_story.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="USA Today preview">{{cite web|title = First impressions: Hands-on with Nintendo 2DS|date = 2013-08-28|publisher = [[Gannett_Company|Gannett Company]]|work = USA Today|last = Molina|first = Brett|url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2013/08/28/nintendo-2ds-impressions/2718421/|accessdate = 2014-05-03|archive-date = 2020-08-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200824054240/https://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2013/08/28/nintendo-2ds-impressions/2718421/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

任天堂2DS使用和常规任天堂3DS系统相同的1300 mAh电源。虽然2DS不支持3DS的制动亮度设定（“省电模式”），但其任天堂标称电池工作时间比3DS略长；任天堂标称2DS一次充电可以游戏3－5.5小时3DS游戏，以及5－9小时DS游戏<ref name="Europe comparison chart">{{cite web|url=http://cdn02.nintendo-europe.com/media/images/projects/flower/3ds/FAMILY_A4_TABLE_UK.pdf|title=Nintendo 3DS family comparison chart|type=PDF|publisher=Nintendo of Europe|accessdate=2013-08-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921054406/http://cdn02.nintendo-europe.com/media/images/projects/flower/3ds/FAMILY_A4_TABLE_UK.pdf|archivedate=2013-09-21}}</ref><ref name="polygon-comparison">{{cite web | url=http://www.polygon.com/2013/8/28/4667962/nintendo-2ds-3ds-comparison | title=Here's how the Nintendo 2DS compares to the 3DS | publisher=Vox Media | work=Polygon | accessdate=2013-08-29 | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112012850/https://www.polygon.com/2013/8/28/4667962/nintendo-2ds-3ds-comparison | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="joystiq-3dspowersave">{{cite web | url=http://www.joystiq.com/2011/01/28/nintendo-3ds-power-save-mode-illuminated/ | title=Nintendo 3DS 'power save mode' illuminated | publisher=AOL | work=Joystiq | accessdate=2013-08-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012145917/http://www.joystiq.com/2011/01/28/nintendo-3ds-power-save-mode-illuminated/ | archive-date=2013-10-12 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

