== 评价 ==
=== 发售前 ===

任天堂2DS在公布时获得了褒贬不一的评价。[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]认为，任天堂2DS可能在一定程度上吸引不会购入任天堂3DS的部分人的市场，这部分人表示出了对[[立体感|立体感]]图形的冷淡<ref name="Kotaku announcement" />。今日美国认为，一些使用裸眼3D思想设计的游戏在没有机能支持的情况下可能难以游玩<ref name="USA Today preview" />。同时CNET也称，该机种表明任天堂承认了3D功能无用甚至是“战略错误”<ref name="CNET announcement" />。《[[NBC新闻|NBC新闻]]》则称发布2DS是为了满足任天堂DS家系玩家的特殊选择。随后表示担心2DS可能从不甚成功的任天堂主机[[Wii_U|Wii U]]上继续抽走战略资源而使得[[Wii_U|Wii U]]的发展更加制限<ref name="NBC News announcement">{{cite web | url=http://www.nbcnews.com/technology/nintendo-announces-new-2ds-mobile-gaming-console-wii-u-price-8C11020758 | title=Nintendo announces new 2DS mobile gaming console, Wii U price drop | publisher=[[NBCUniversal|NBCUniversal]] Media | work=[[NBCNews.com|NBCNews.com]] | date=2013-08-28 | last=LeJacq | first=Yannick | accessdate=2014-05-03 | archive-date=2020-11-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111204430/https://www.nbcnews.com/technology/nintendo-announces-new-2ds-mobile-gaming-console-wii-u-price-8C11020758 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

一些技术类作者对2DS的物理外观表示关注：CNET认为游戏机比[[任天堂3DS家族|其他机型]]难看的多<ref name="CNET announcement">{{cite web | url=http://reviews.cnet.com/consoles/nintendo-2ds-blue/4505-10109_7-35826997.html | title=Nintendo 2DS drops a dimension and price, coming October 12 for $129 | publisher=CBS Interactive | work=CNET | date=2013-08-28 | last=Stein | first=Scott | access-date=2014-05-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140318071604/http://reviews.cnet.com/consoles/nintendo-2ds-blue/4505-10109_7-35826997.html | archive-date=2014-03-18 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>，但一些评论者则通常称其舒适易持。《美国今日》称其“出奇的舒适”<ref name="USA Today preview" />。Kotaku认为尽管主机看着笨重，但即使用单手也能舒适握持。Kotaku还称主机按钮易于操作，将按键置于游戏机上半部分能引导眼睛看着上屏。Kotaku总体认为任天堂2DS构造品質良好<ref name="Kotaku announcement" />。GamesIndustry也称任天堂2DS的操作比之前机种更为舒适。评论还认为任天堂2DS不同于薄壳的任天堂3DS，而是使用了厚壳，取消转轴构造让游戏机更耐用。他们认为其设计就像“[[Game_Boy|Game Boy]]、[[Wii_U游戏控制器|Wii U游戏控制器]]和DS的可怕结合”<ref name="GamesIndustry announcement">{{cite web | url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2013-08-28-nintendo-cuts-wii-u-by-USD50-announces-2ds-handheld | title=Nintendo cuts Wii U by $50, announces 2DS handheld &#124 | publisher=Gamer Network | work=GamesIndustry International | date=2013-04-19 | accessdate=2013-08-30 | last=Parish | first=Jeremy | archive-date=2020-06-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200603075706/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2013-08-28-nintendo-cuts-wii-u-by-USD50-announces-2ds-handheld | dead-url=no }}</ref>。因为没有可闭合翻盖，《美国今日》和CNET都对屏幕保护方式表示担忧<ref name="CNET announcement" /><ref name="USA Today preview" />。

在关于任天堂2DS以单物理显示屏模拟双屏的回应中，Ars Technica的凯尔·奥兰多认为，任天堂错过了使用2DS外形制作全屏游戏[[平板电脑|平板]]的机会；奥兰多称，这本可让未来游戏与应用程序使用整个屏幕区域，并继续兼容之前为可折叠3DS和DS设计的游戏，同时提升移植既有[[智能手机|智能手机]]游戏的能力。但奥兰多也称，引入这种产品可能打乱任天堂便携式游戏生态系（即现在的3DS用户）——这对于3DS的周期，即任天堂引入次世代机种，而言为时过早<ref name="ars" />。

《连线》称为低价销售而重设计任天堂3DS是“明智之举”，杂志称2DS可能会是任天堂以相当的低价销售，从而大幅获利<ref name="Wired announcement">{{cite web | url=http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2013/08/nintendo-2ds/ | title=Nintendo’s Weird New 2DS Proves It: Price Is Always the Problem | publisher=Condé Nast Digital | work=Wired | date=2013-08-28 | last=Kohler | first=Chris | accessdate=2014-05-03 | archive-date=2014-03-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140328223807/http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2013/08/nintendo-2ds | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 发售后 ===

任天堂2DS获得褒贬不一的评价。虽然评论认为其售价和外形理想，但其美学和电池工作时间获得广泛批评。电讯报认为，取消翻盖转轴设计让其更为耐用，脚印版的圆滑让儿童握持更理想。然而评论批评道，主机的单声道扬声器使其声音品質较之前机种下降。他们还称电池续航时间和原3DS机种相同。然而他们称赞屏幕更亮且可视角度更广，虽然它并没有3DS XL那么大<ref name="telegraph review">{{cite web|last=Robertson|first=Andy|title=Nintendo 2DS review|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/video-game-reviews/10356259/Nintendo-2DS-review.html|publisher=The Telegraph|accessdate=2013-11-09|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629032129/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/video-game-reviews/10356259/Nintendo-2DS-review.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]称，任天堂2DS并非针对“经验丰富的玩家”或目前的任天堂3DS机主，并认为系统生产未充分考虑美学。评论还批评过时的电阻式触摸屏，单声道扬声器以及电池续航时间。不过Eurogamer认为系统比任天堂3DS和3DS XL拿着更为舒适<ref name="eurogamer review">{{cite web | url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/digitalfoundry-nintendo-2ds-review | title=Nintendo 2DS review | publisher=Gamer Network | work=Eurogamer | accessdate=2013-11-09 | last=McFerran | first=Damien | archive-date=2019-12-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212091920/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/digitalfoundry-nintendo-2ds-review | dead-url=no }}</ref>。分析师皮尔斯·哈丁-罗尔斯认为，任天堂2DS帮助任天堂扩大市场，并认为[[第三方开发商|第三方发行商]]将为平台前进做出更多承诺<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nbcnews.com/technology/nintendo-puts-itself-back-game-2ds-pokemon-x-y-8C11381602 | title=Nintendo puts itself back in the game with 2DS and 'Pokémon X & Y' | publisher=NBCUniversal Media | work=NBCNews.com | accessdate=2013-11-09 | archive-date=2020-11-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111195441/https://www.nbcnews.com/technology/nintendo-puts-itself-back-game-2ds-pokemon-x-y-8C11381602 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

随着系统推出，任天堂表示。号称“必玩”作品的《[[索尼克_失落的世界|索尼克 失落的世界]]》的发行会推动任天堂2DS的销售<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/nintendo-sonic-will-help-drive-2ds-sales/ | title=Nintendo: Sonic will help drive 2DS sales | publisher=Intent Media | work=MCV UK | accessdate=2013-11-09 | archive-date=2016-10-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161028215609/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/nintendo-sonic-will-help-drive-2ds-sales/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。任天堂总裁[[岩田聪|岩田聪]]在2013年10月31日坦言，任天堂2DS在准买家中知晓度不足。此外他还表示，一些潜在客户认为产品带着过于笨重。但岩田聪表示，系统获得购买者的积极评价<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.shacknews.com/article/81839/nintendo-admits-2ds-awareness-is-too-low | title=Nintendo admits 2DS 'awareness' is too low | publisher=GameFly | work=ShackNews.com | accessdate=2013-11-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105120710/http://www.shacknews.com/article/81839/nintendo-admits-2ds-awareness-is-too-low | archive-date=2013-11-05 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。虽然2DS不支持3D显示，但岩田聪在任天堂2013年第三季度的投资者问答中坚称，公司“不会放弃3D或停止3D显示的新主张”，他会继续销售现有的任天堂3DS和3DS XL平台<ref name="3d future">{{cite web | url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/436850/nintendo-not-abandoning-3d-despite-2ds-release-says-iwata/ | title=Nintendo not abandoning 3D despite 2DS release, says Iwata | publisher=Future plc | work=CVG | accessdate=2013-11-09 | archive-date=2015-02-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150219070235/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/436850/nintendo-not-abandoning-3d-despite-2ds-release-says-iwata/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。但《[[塞尔达传说_众神的三角力量2|塞尔达传说 众神的三角力量2]]》制作人[[青沼英二|青沼英二]]在采访中透漏，游戏开发时为不支持3D的2DS做了小调整<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-legend-of-zelda-a-link-between-worlds-changed-slightly-because-of-2ds/1100-6415659/ | title=The Legend of Zelda: A Link Between Worlds changed slightly because of 2DS | publisher=CBS Interactive | work=GameSpot | accessdate=2013-11-24 | last=Gaston | first=Martin | archive-date=2013-12-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131201024338/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-legend-of-zelda-a-link-between-worlds-changed-slightly-because-of-2ds/1100-6415659/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 销量 ===

任天堂2DS在英国发售三周后，零售商因低销量而降价，致使其销量猛增。系统可以约110英镑的售价够得，但[[Argos|Argos]]、[[Amazon.com|亚马逊]]和[[Tesco|Tesco]]等主要零售商为迎合学校期中假，将系统售价降至100英镑以下<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.expertreviews.co.uk/games/1303309/nintendo-2ds-price-slashed-to-below-100 | title=Nintendo 2DS price slashed to below £100 | publisher=Dennis Publishing Limited | work=Expert Reviews | accessdate=2013-11-24 | last=Halfacree | first=Gareth | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131205182548/http://www.expertreviews.co.uk/games/1303309/nintendo-2ds-price-slashed-to-below-100 | archive-date=2013-12-05 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。此举使任天堂2DS周销量环比增长64%，使其成为英国当月最畅销游戏机（将其独立于[[任天堂3DS|任天堂3DS]]和[[任天堂3DS_XL|3DS XL]]计算）<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/2ds-enjoys-half-term-sales-spike/0123618 | title=2DS enjoys half-term sales spike | publisher=Intent Media | work=MCV UK | accessdate=2013-11-06 | last=Dring | first=Christopher | archive-date=2013-11-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105002254/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/2ds-enjoys-half-term-sales-spike/0123618 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2013年第三季度中，游戏零售商巨头[[GameStop|GameStop]]报告称，主因任天堂2DS和3DS的强大销量，全球硬件销量增长了15.3%<ref>{{cite web|last=Liebl|first=Matt|title=GTA 5, Nintendo 2DS boost GameStop sales for Q3 2013|url=http://www.gamezone.com/news/2013/11/21/gta-5-nintendo-2ds-boost-gamestop-sales-for-q3-2013|publisher=GameZone|accessdate=2013-11-24|archive-date=2014-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203100338/http://www.gamezone.com/news/2013/11/21/gta-5-nintendo-2ds-boost-gamestop-sales-for-q3-2013|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

